Detailed Description

KINE+ child object enumerator.

Child/Descendant Node Enumeration Object

Use this object to query for child or descendant nodes of a given object. An instance of this class may only be created with either IKineNode::EnumChildren or IKineNode::EnumAllDescendants to enumerate, responsibly, direct child or all descendant nodes.
